      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison metrics were computed for all five operating points. Agreement was within experimental uncertainty at four of five conditions. The fifth condition showed an 18% overprediction; the team noted this is within the known scatter of hemolysis model predictions in the literature and that the overprediction is conservative relative to the clinical threshold. Validation uncertainty was estimated but not fully propagated through the hemolysis model chain."
